itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"造新聞嚟抄高啲雞價？ 咁益啲姊妹呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f7e124ed562dac215aaa6b28c597e642e315a6","tid":877041,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"10萬屌幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}